trans-unit.source: How do I rename a Team Project?
trans-unit.target: How do I rename a Team Project?

trans-unit.source: A team project rename updates all of your version control paths, work items, queries, and other team project artifacts to reflect the new name.
trans-unit.target: A team project rename updates all of your version control paths, work items, queries, and other team project artifacts to reflect the new name.

trans-unit.source: Team projects can be renamed multiple times and older names can be reused as well.
trans-unit.target: Team projects can be renamed multiple times and older names can be reused as well.

trans-unit.source: Post rename, there might be some action required from team members.
trans-unit.target: Post rename, there might be some action required from team members.

trans-unit.source: It is recommended to perform this action during off-hours to minimize any impact.
trans-unit.target: It is recommended to perform this action during off-hours to minimize any impact.

trans-unit.source: Please see renaming a team project for more information.
trans-unit.target: Please see renaming a team project for more information.
